title: Ladies Doctor, Il Ginecologo Della Mutua

sources.title: Ladies Doctor, Il Ginecologo Della Mutua
sources.description: Lots of familiar faces in this one, Renzo Montagnani, Paola Senatore, Marina Hedman. Plot has something to do with a gynecologist who owes money high tailing it out of town and leaving his practice in the care of Renzo. Not sure if he ever gets any work done. Italian with optional English Subtitles Â
